      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AVENGEMENT (8) first attempt at the staying journey. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Rates highly and will give a great sight. JONI BLACK (4) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from six starts. In the money last time at Sandown (34.49) in a Grade 5, finishing a 1.75 lengths second. Looks suited here and can measure up. IRISH MILLIE (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (42.96) in a S/E Group 1 at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Likely to be about the mark. GREYSYND SAMMY (1) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
